snippet.title: Greg Hastings Paintball 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out Bas Rutten's Liver Shot on MMA Surge: http://bit.ly/MMASurgeEp1
http://www.mahalo.com/greg-hastings-paintball-2

Check out our other Greg Hastings Paintball 2 videos: http://www.youtube.com/view_play_list?p=A5F35B68858D50B3

Greg Hastings is back in this new go-round on the paintball field. Battle across 62 unique fields in 12 real-life locations. With improved weather dynamics, map editor and 10 v. 10 online play, it's a sure way to get some of the excitement of paintballing at home.
